#GoodNewsTues: a new paper in @ScienceMagazine shows that phytoplankton (tiny plants) in the Arctic Ocean are increasing in number, which may give us a future #ArcticOcean that can support a more robust food web and export more carbon to the deep ocean! https://t.co/jEa05q9LuH https://t.co/Muz94oIiO7
